snippet.textDisplay:
• No Best Software Experience award?
Many of them are still not putting enough effort in improving the digital experience imo

• No Most Ethical, Sustainable or Socially Responsible award?
It’s 2019, probably a good time to start talking about who is actually trying to make the game better for all...would be very interesting and a great journalistic effort to figure out who is trying to manufacture better, who is reducing their profit in order to make progress more affordable...not interested in a $300 phone if it means using slave labor or a $1000 if it means 75% go to company shareholders...

• No Most Durable/Accident Proof Award?
So much money for beautiful designs that users now find normal to cover with stupid cases...even though every year everybody claim having the “toughest glass” and all...remember how waterproofing actually changed people’s life?!!

Still love your content tho, keep it up 🙌
